reviewText: Rood uses some footage from previous works and adds more to it. I liked his presentation. Hi voice is animated and his presentation holds your attention. If you have interest in the Moses Exodus, you can't go wrong with this. There other good videos on this subject. They are all excellent. My hat is off to them all.
A little short with an invitation to invest in further discoveries.
The content was great, the delivery was disappointing.
This confirmed some info I already had, but added to it. Good stuff.
Expensive for a 25 minute video, not enough footage of artifacts, very disappointed with this purchase. I would not purchase again!
This is an excellent factual teaching. Anyone wishing to learn about the true account of the red Sea crossing should start here. Michael Rood bring this to life as only he can.
This DVD clearly teaches the historic accuracy of the Red Sea crossing by the ancient Israelite s, exposing the wreckage of the Egyptian Pharaoh's great army still at the bottom of the sea.

All these years of the official line that emphatically stated that Israel was never resident in Egypt and never left there en masse. This video has verifiable video footage of the Egyptian army chariots scattered on the floor of the gulf where the waters were divided. But don't let me sway you. Just look at the evidence. But be willing to believe facts as opposed to traditional truisms.
